{"tid":2288441,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本：以平權及環保作賣點的拜登 在香港問題上會更強硬","createTime":"2020-11-16T13:08:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T13:32:51.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7105e7dd0ab938def9199ac358ec5d3ac63ab59f","tid":2288441,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T13:08:39.000Z","msg":"日外相料拜登在香港問題上比特朗普更強硬 <br />\n<br />\n日本外相茂木敏充在東京出席日本記者協會活動，談及區域安全問題，呼籲中國負起大國責任，強調日本會堅決阻止中國在東海及南海地區，企圖以武力單方面改變現狀。 <br />\n<br />\n茂木說，美國總統大選後，中美的對立關係不會即時解除，認為即使是拜登上台，在貿易等方面，中美會繼續出現嚴重對立。但他指，中美仍然可以在氣候變化及全球公共衛生等議題上合作，但預期在人權、香港及新疆等問題上，拜登政府的態度可能比特朗普政府更強硬。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/china/2366547\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F2366547&d=Mbax9TUBBsNKvtRo7%2B5fu4dddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=880a929f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/china/2366547</a>"},{"pid":"ae8e2828a0d67d4cc5264e2d84e95bc576baa752","tid":2288441,"uid":77717,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T13:09:46.000Z","msg":"民主黨進步派=共產黨<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2287804\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2287804</a>"},{"pid":"34e059cef7da812d83b60635b21b8e1346b12bb2","tid":2288441,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T13:09:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dabeaebbd158a3d4bc894cf2d9a4e83f0d1163ba","tid":2288441,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T13:09:58.000Z","msg":"Harris:  let's scroll up sleeves and work harder <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa5ee68710115619d0eee1af7c7f72277180ed3f","tid":2288441,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T13:10:23.000Z","msg":"C&rsquo;mon man